                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13984315" author="mduerig" created="Tue, 29 Apr 2014 14:03:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The most visible symptom of this regression is the &lt;tt&gt;DiffCache&lt;/tt&gt; not being properly populated, as per &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mreutegg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mreutegg&quot;&gt;mreutegg&lt;/a&gt; branch commits do not go into that cache. Therefore for some observation scenarios the hit rate of this cache is as low as 5% but never higher than 50%. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13984326" author="mduerig" created="Tue, 29 Apr 2014 14:08:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch that only does the purge when the underlying branch has already been created. This patch increases the hit rate of the case to &amp;gt;90%. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13985655" author="mduerig" created="Wed, 30 Apr 2014 15:52:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in trunk at 1591362&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13985671" author="mduerig" created="Wed, 30 Apr 2014 16:14:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in 1.0 branch at &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1591382&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1591382&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14017588" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Wed, 4 Jun 2014 10:16:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;bulk close for the 1.0 release&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
